Java Solution

You can use the below code as the solution to your problem but it is not the optimized code. After some test cases, it shows the TLE.

Optimize solution is written below

class Solution {
    // function to return sum of  1, 2, ... n
    long seriesSum(int n) {
        int a = 0;
        while (n>0)
        {
            a = a+n;
            n--;
        }
        return a;
    }
}

//

Optimized Solution

class Solution {
    // function to return the sum of  1, 2, ... n
    long seriesSum(int n) {
        long s = ((long)n*(long)(n+1))/2;
        return s;
    }
}

//
